{"tid":1775563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區選投票率新高 政府:證明市民厭倦示威活動","createTime":"2019-12-09T02:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T02:41:45.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ebf6075fe44243ea83a35e43abfcedf1c601088","tid":1775563,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:39:14.000Z","msg":"80萬人大遊行 又出黎話代表市民反暴力 民意逆轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445c7c9719787fa108495d0460f6e403f1ebd636","tid":1775563,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebea7bc616fb2d563d21744525733cbcc1816433","tid":1775563,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:39:52.000Z","msg":"人民日報評論稱昨日遊行大致和平 市民或對暴力厭倦<br />\n《人民日報》發表評論員文章，提到昨日的民陣遊行，過程大致和平有序，暴力破壞活動有所收斂，認為香港市民或正以自己的言行表達對暴力的厭倦。<br />\n<br />\n文章又說，黑衣暴徒再次偏離遊行路線，堆積雜物堵路，又破壞商鋪與警方對峙，更在香港終審法院、高等法院門前縱火，顯示了暴徒勢要「攬炒」的野心，認為市民應當清醒，驅散謊言與暴力，將和平理性表達訴求的市民與違法作亂的暴徒區分開來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529d6645c4d7dbf22c08a05991e728d0b2a7cccb","tid":1775563,"uid":94241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"呃唔到香港人 但呃哂中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}